MosDNS is a DNS forwarder with flexible configuration capabilities.

This OPNsense plugin provides:
- Web-based configuration interface for MosDNS
- Service management (start/stop/restart)
- YAML configuration editing through forms
- Real-time status monitoring
- Log viewing capabilities
- Support for multiple upstream DNS servers
- Plugin-based architecture configuration

MosDNS supports various DNS protocols including:
- Traditional UDP/TCP DNS
- DNS over HTTPS (DoH)
- DNS over TLS (DoT)

The plugin integrates seamlessly with OPNsense's service management
system and provides an intuitive interface for managing DNS forwarding
rules and upstream server configurations.

WWW: https://github.com/IrineSistiana/mosdns